  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK568">
<l>iṉattāṟṟi yeṇṇāta vēntaṉ ciṉattāṟṟic </l>
<l> cīṟiṟ ciṟukun tiru</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The prosperity of that king will waste away, who without reflecting (on his affairs himself), commits them to his ministers, and (when a failure occurs) gives way to anger, and rages against them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
